<connector> <property name="%ID" sourceProperty="ID" description="Record ID" /> <property name="mTS" sourceProperty="DateTime" type="%TimeStamp" description="Measurement DateTime"/> <property name="PerfGloRef" sourceProperty="Perf_GloRef" type="%Numeric" description="Global - local references"/> <property name="PerfGloUpdate" sourceProperty="Perf_GloUpdate" type="%Numeric" description="Global - local updates (set / kill)"/> <property name="PerfGloRefRem" sourceProperty="Perf_GloRefRem" type="%Numeric" description="Global - remote references"/> <property name="PerfGloUpdateRem" sourceProperty="Perf_GloUpdateRem" type="%Numeric" description="Global - remote updates (set / kill)"/> <property name="PerfPhysReads" sourceProperty="Perf_PhysReads" type="%Numeric" description="Global - physical reads" /> <property name="PerfPhysWrites" sourceProperty="Perf_PhysWrites" type="%Numeric" description="Global - physical writes"/> <property name="PerfLogReads" sourceProperty="Perf_LogReads" type="%Numeric" description="Logical database reads"/>
<property name="PerfRtnCallLocal" sourceProperty="Perf_RtnCallLocal" type="%Numeric" description="Routines - local calls"/> <property name="PerfRtnCallRemote" sourceProperty="Perf_RtnCallRemote" type="%Numeric" description="Routines - remote calls"/> <property name="PerfRtnLoad" sourceProperty="Perf_RtnLoad" type="%Numeric" description="Routines - local loads and saves to disc"/> <property name="PerfRtnLoadRem" sourceProperty="Perf_RtnLoadRem" type="%Numeric" description="Routines - remote loads and saves to disc"/>
<property name="PerfWIJWrites" sourceProperty="Perf_WIJWrites" type="%Numeric" description="WIJ - physical block writes"/>
<property name="PerfObjLoad" sourceProperty="Perf_ObjLoad" type="%Numeric" description="Object loaded from disc"/> <property name="PerfObjHit" sourceProperty="Perf_ObjHit" type="%Numeric" description="Object references (found in memory)"/> <property name="PerfObjMiss" sourceProperty="Perf_ObjMiss" type="%Numeric" description="Object references (not in memory)"/> <property name="PerfObjNew" sourceProperty="Perf_ObjNew" type="%Numeric" description="Object initialized"/> <property name="PerfObjDel" sourceProperty="Perf_ObjDel" type="%Numeric" description="Object deleted"/>
<property name="PerfECPBlockAdd" sourceProperty="Perf_ECPBlockAdd" type="%Numeric" description="ECP - block added to cache"/> <property name="PerfECPBlockPurgeBuff" sourceProperty="Perf_ECPBlockPurgeBuff" type="%Numeric" description="ECP - block purged from buffer"/> <property name="PerfECPBlockPurgeSvr" sourceProperty="Perf_ECPBlockPurgeSvr" type="%Numeric" description="ECP - block rurge by server request"/> <property name="PerfECPByteRcvd" sourceProperty="Perf_ECPByteRcvd" type="%Numeric" description="ECP - bytes received"/> <property name="PerfECPByteSent" sourceProperty="Perf_ECPByteSent" type="%Numeric" description="ECP - bytes sent"/> <property name="PerfECPConn" sourceProperty="Perf_ECPConn" type="%Numeric" description="ECP - active connections"/>

<property name="PerfJrnBlock" sourceProperty="Perf_JrnBlock" type="%Numeric" description="Journal - blocks written to disc"/> <property name="PerfJrnEntry" sourceProperty="Perf_JrnEntry" type="%Numeric" description="Journal - number of entries created"/> </connector>
